{"tid":1653593,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［代朋友出post] ［前線］深深感受到被出賣嘅感覺","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:26:01.000Z","uid":45772,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed0e7ed95a79db5ef4fdaf4bd3ab147931ae908","tid":1653593,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"代朋友出post <br />\n尋日約咗兩點去一齊去深水埗行街<br />\n大家一直都冇共識<br />\n有啲人話想去楓樹街球場坐陣<br />\n有啲人就話想去長沙灣政府合署附近等齊人先行街<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個唔係重點<br />\n重點係兩個地方，夾埋都唔過50人<br />\n大家鳩行咗一陣<br />\n到三點半左右，有好多警車冇響警號，突然衝左去長沙灣政府合署個十字路口，但我哋得20人，啲警察無緣無故追住我哋，根本反應唔切。 而班街坊全部都食花生睇戲。<br />\n<br />\n結果20人有10幾個比人拉咗<br />\n<br />\n原來大家都係得個講字<br />\n原來大家都咁鍾意留係屋企食花生<br />\n原來大家原先話一齊行街，結果大部份人都放飛機<br />\n<br />\n在此呼籲大家以後唔好再出去<br />\n香港冇得救㗎喇"},{"pid":"a58d576c16bc6c29559d2e26c48e66c520a31ee7","tid":1653593,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b419190646b36a19d6d0185436d4938ab451a","tid":1653593,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"屌你哋老母臭閪"},{"pid":"13c61458d0ab9a6646743a510c0f5e5ba8704c51","tid":1653593,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"可以檢討 但不要棄餒<br />\n可以批評 但不要謾罵"},{"pid":"f11f4ae02c104c251ab655db914e92b3fefbcbc5","tid":1653593,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58d576c16bc6c29559d2e26c48e66c520a31ee7","tid":1653593,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331ef4820ec09a72c7c3cb5df7e7834c346a0a30","tid":1653593,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"5，6區好過分咁多區"},{"pid":"0939b6799390f7e0e52f126dcbcbb8d205d9410a","tid":1653593,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"咁多區人少"},{"pid":"8608834e2b6389df225dbce7e37f96034349dc5c","tid":1653593,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"咪屈 問題係太分散"},{"pid":"0dfd6d793df400e9b574cba2be2a7718265c17d2","tid":1653593,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:18:17.000Z","msg":"太少人喇 和理非街坊無哂影<br />\n得返班前線岀嚟<br />\n講緊每個區過千人都無"},{"pid":"e13542f8ecee80b2acdcfae2b163fd1fa2ce6e63","tid":1653593,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"分散果個重點係, 除左18區分散外<br />\n深水埗區自己都分散<br />\n集合地點一直唔明確, 有v walk (唔該唔好再吹雞v walk) / 楓樹街遊樂場/ 長沙灣運動場 / 政府合署十字路口<br />\n我原本係諗住街坊進場, 但係十九幾萬個集合地我根本唔知去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出去行都未撚行到集合地, 未知邊度開花, 亦都未開始, 就話好多人俾人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08cf3bcc41a8351da6ccc825143c7e8183c6fae","tid":1653593,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"好撚煩吊你老母 係咁講香港人點失敗 你有沒出過黎呀幫手吊你老母"},{"pid":"8d20ecb7f2f0b8c4a0f75294ffb6e3386318cb3f","tid":1653593,"uid":188448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"琴日真心灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔割席啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}